text:
All mammals except primates can instinctively swim.
Primate infants can also instinctively swim, but for some reason they lose the ability.

Also we are not 100% sure if giraffe s can swim, because it's hard to justify doing the experiment, and it never comes up in the wild.

Bat's swimming is kinda cool as a thing
